descriptionHtml:
2 floors.
has no known bugs.
has very little decorations. (food, plates, cups, etc)
its a simple house in river-wood.
this is my first mod so please rate it nicely :) I tried to avoid webbing and over laps, etc. I will be adding decorations and stuff but for now there is only chairs and stuff. you may edit the file but if you distribute the file please credit.. you don\'t need permission just credit me. I will be making a more detailed house this week and next, so please add in some suggestions. i am also working on making weapons and stuff ( but only recoloring stuff or making simple objects) please just hit me up a suggestion i am happy to try!
author: bangyomom
